quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  19,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  19,1,Kaaaf-Haa-Yaa-'Ayyyn-Saaad
  19,2,Zikru rahmati Rabbika 'abdahoo Zakariyya
  19,3,Iz naadaa Rabbahoo nidaaa'an khafiyyaa
  19,4,Qaala Rabbi innee wahanal'azmu minnee washta'alar raasu shaibanw wa lam akum bidu'aaa'ika Rabbi shaqiyyaa
  19,5,Wa innee khiftul mawaa liya minw waraaa'ee wa kaana tim ra atee 'aairan fahab lee mil ladunka waliyyaa
  19,6,"Yarisunee wa yarisu min aali Ya'qoob, waj'alhu Rabbi radiyya"
  19,7,Yaa Zakariyyaaa innaa nubashshiruka bighulaami nismuhoo Yahyaa lam naj'al lahoo min qablu samiyyaa
  19,8,Qaala Rabbi annaa yakoonu lee ghulaamunw wa kaanatim ra atee aaqiranw wa qad balaghtu minal kibari 'itiyyaa
  19,9,Qaala kazaalika qaala Rabbuka huwa 'alaiya haiyinunw wa qad khalaqtuka min qablu wa lam taku shai'aa
  19,10,Qaala Rabbij 'al leee Aayah; qaala Aayatuka allaa tukalliman naasa salaasa layaalin sawiyyaa
  19,11,Fakharaja 'alaa qawmihee minal mihraabi fa-awhaaa ilaihim an sabbihoo bukratanw wa 'ashiyyaa
  19,12,Yaa Yahyaa khuzil Kitaaba biquwwatinw wa aatainaahul hukma saiyyaa
  19,13,Wa hanaanam mil ladunnaa wa zakaatanw wa kaana taqiyyaa
  19,14,Wa barram biwaalidayhi wa lam yakum jabbaaran 'asiyyaa
  19,15,Wa salaamun 'alaihi yawma wulida wa yawma yamootu wa yawma yub'asu haiyaa (section 1)
  19,16,Wazkur fil Kitaabi Marya; izin tabazat min ahlihaa makaanan shariqyyaa
  19,17,Fattakhazat min doonihim hijaaban fa arsalnaaa ilaihaa roohanaa fatamassala lahaa basharan sawiyyaa
  19,18,Qaalat inneee a'oozu bir Rahmaani minka in kunta taqiyyaa
  19,19,Qaala innamaa ana rasoolu Rabbiki li ahaba laki ghulaaman zakiyyaa
  19,20,Qaalat anna yakoonu lee ghulaamunw wa lam yamsasnee bashrunw wa lam aku baghiyyaa
  19,21,Qaala kazaaliki qaala Rabbuki huwa 'alaiya yaiyimunw wa linaj 'alahooo Aayatal linnaasi wa rahmatam minnaa; wa kaana amram maqdiyyaa
  19,22,Fahamalat hu fantabazat bihee makaanan qasiyyaa
  19,23,Fa ajaaa 'ahal makhaadu ilaa jiz'in nakhlati qaalat yaa laitanee mittu qabla haazaa wa kuntu nasyam mansiyyaa
  19,24,Fanaadaahaa min tahtihaan allaa tahzanee qad ja'ala Rabbuki tahtaki sariyyaa
  19,25,Wa huzzeee ilaiki bijiz 'in nakhlati tusaaqit 'alaiki rutaban janiyyaa
  19,26,Fakulee washrabee wa qarree 'ainaa; fa immaa tarayinnna minal bashari ahadan faqooleee innee nazartu lir Rahmaani sawman falan ukallimal yawma insiyyaa
  19,27,Fa atat bihee qawmahaa tahmiluhoo qaaloo yaa Maryamoo laqad ji'ti shai'an fariyyaa
  19,28,Yaaa ukkhta Haaroona maa kaana abokim ra-a saw'inw wa maa kaanat ummuki baghiyyaa
  19,29,Fa ashaarat ilaih; qaaloo kaifa nukallimu man kaana fil mahdi sabiyyaa
  19,30,Qaala innee 'abdullaahi aataaniyal Kitaaba wa ja'alanee Nabiyyaa
  19,31,Wa ja'alanee mubaarakan aina maa kuntu wa awsaanee bis Salaati waz Zakaati maa dumtu haiyaa
  19,32,Wa barram biwaalidatee wa lam yaj'alnee jabbaaran shaqiyyaa
  19,33,Wassalaamu 'alaiya yawma wulittu wa yawma amootu wa yawma ub'asu baiyaa
  19,34,Zaalika 'Eesab-nu Marya; qawlal haqqil lazee feehi yamtaroon
  19,35,Maa kaana lillaahi ai yattakhiza minw waladin Subhaanah; izaa qadaaa amran fa innamaa yaqoolu lahoo kun fa yakoon
  19,36,Wa innal laaha Rabbee wa Rabbukum fa'budooh; haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem
  19,37,Fakhtalafal ahzaabu mim bainihim fawailul lillazeena kafaroo mim mashhadi Yawmin 'azeem
  19,38,Asmi' bihim wa absir Yawma yaatoonanaa laakiniz zaalimoonal yawma fee dalaalim mubeen
  19,39,Wa anzirhum Yawmal hasrati iz qudiyal amr; wa hum fee ghaflatinw wa hum laa yu'minoon
  19,40,Innaa NNahnu narisul arda wa man 'alaihaa wa ilainaa yurja'oon (section 2)
  19,41,Wazkur fil Kitaabi Ibraaheem; innahoo kaana siddeeqan Nabiyyaa
  19,42,Iz qaala li abeehi yaaa abati lima ta'budu maa laa yasma'u wa laa yubsiru wa laa yughnee 'anka shai'aa
  19,43,Yaaa abati innee qad jaaa'anee minal 'ilmi maa lam yaatika fattabi'neee ahdika siraatan Sawiyyaa
  19,44,Yaaa abati laa ta'budish Shaitaana innash Shaitaana kaana lir Rahmaani 'asiyyaa
  19,45,Yaaa abati innee akhaafu ai yamssaka 'azaabum minar Rahmaani fatakoona lish Shaitaani waliyyaa
  19,46,Qaala araaghibun anta 'an aalihatee yaaa Ibraaheemu la 'il lam tantahi la arjumannaka wahjumee maliyyaa
  19,47,Qaala salaamun 'alaika sa astaghfiru laka Rabbeee innahoo kaana bee hafiyyaa
  19,48,Wa a'tazilukum wa maa tad'oona min doonil laahi wa ad'o Rabbee 'asaaa allaaa akoona bidu'aaa'i Rabbee shaqiyyaa
  19,49,"Falamma' tazalahum wa maa ya'budoona min doonil laahi wahabnaa lahoo is-haaqa wa ya'qoob, wa kullan ja'alnaa Nabiyyaa"
  19,50,Wa wahabnaa lahum mirrahmatinaa wa ja'alnaa lahum lisaana sidqin 'aliyyaa (section 3)
  19,51,Wazkur fil Kitaabi Moosaaa; innahoo kaana mukhlasanw wa kaana Rasoolan Nabiyyaa
  19,52,Wa naadainaahu min jaanibit Tooril aimani wa qarrabnaahu najiyyaa
  19,53,Wa wahabnaa lahoo mir rahmatinaaa akhaahu Haaroona Nabiyyaa
  19,54,Wazkur fil Kitaabi ismaa'eel; innahoo kaana saadiqal wa'di wa kaana Rasoolan Nabiyyaa
  19,55,Wa kaana yaamuru ahlahoo bis Salaati waz zakaati wa kaana 'inda Rabbihee mardiyyaa
  19,56,Wazkur fil Kitaabi Idrees; innahoo kaana siddeeqan Nabiyyaa
  19,57,Wa rafa'naahu makaanan 'aliyyaa
  19,58,Ulaaa'ikal lazeena an'amal laahu 'alaihim minan Nabiyyeena min zurriyyati Aadama wa mimman hamalnaa ma'a Noohinw wa min zurriyyati Ibraaheema wa Israaa'eela wa mimman hadainaa wajta bainaaa; izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatur Rahmaani kharroo sujjadanw wa bukiyyaa�(make sajda)
  19,59,Fakhalafa mim ba'dihim khalfun adaa'us Salaata wattaba'ush shahawaati fasawfa yalqawna ghaiyaa
  19,60,Illaa man taaba wa aamana wa 'amila saalihan fa ulaaa'ika yadkhuloonal jannata wa laa yuzlamoona shai'aa
  19,61,Jannaati 'adninil latee wa'adar Rahmaanu ibaadahoo bilghaib; innahoo kaana wa'duhoo maatiyyaa
  19,62,Laa yasma'oona feehaa laghwan illaa salaamaa; wa lahum rizquhum feehaa bukratanw wa 'ashiyyaa
  19,63,Tilkal jannatul latee oorisu min 'ibaadinaa man kaana taqiyyaa
  19,64,Wa maa natanazzalu illaa bi amri Rabbika lahoo maa baina aideenaa wa maa khalfanaa wa maa baina zaalik; wa maa kaana Rabbuka nasiyyaa
  19,65,Rabbus samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumaa fa'bud hu wastabir li'ibaadatih; hal ta'lamu lahoo samiyyaa (section 4)
  19,66,Wa yaqoolul insaanu 'aizaa maa mittu lasawfa ukhraju haiyaa
  19,67,awalaa yazkurul insaanu annaa khalaqnaahu min qablu wa lam yaku shai'aa
  19,68,Fawa Rabbika lanahshu rannahum wash shayaateena summa lanuhdirannahum hawla jahannama jisiyyaa
  19,69,Summa lananzi 'anna min kulli shee'atin aiyuhum ashaddu 'alar Rahmaani 'itiyyaa
  19,70,Summa lanahnu a'lamu billazeena hum awlaa bihaa siliyyaa
  19,71,Wa im minkum illaa waa riduhaa; kaana 'alaa Rabbika hatmam maqdiyyaa
  19,72,Summa nunajjil lazeenat taqaw wa nazaruz zaalimeena feehaa jisiyyaa
  19,73,Wa izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatunaa baiyinaatin qaalal lazeena kafaroo lillazeena aamanooo aiyul fareeqaini khairum maqaamanw wa ahsanu nadiyyaa
  19,74,Wa kam ahlaknaa qablahum min qarnin hum ahsanu asaasanw wa ri'yaa
  19,75,Qul man kaana fidda laalati falyamdud lahur Rahmaanu maddaa; hattaaa izaa ra aw maa yoo'adoona immal 'azaaba wa immas Saa'ata fasa ya'lamoona man huwa sharrum makaananw wa ad'afu jundaa
  19,76,Wa yazeedul laahul lazeenah tadaw hudaa; wal baaqiyaatus saalihaatu khairun 'inda Rabbika sawaabanw wa khairum maraddaa
  19,77,Afara'aytal lazee kafara bi Aayaatinaa wa qaala la oota yanna maalanw wa waladaa
  19,78,Attala'al ghaiba amitta khaza'indar Rahmaani 'ahdaa
  19,79,Kallaa; sanaktubu maa yaqoolu wa namuddu lahoo minal 'azaabi maddaa
  19,80,Wa narisuhoo maa yaqoolu wa yaateenaa fardaa
  19,81,Wattakhazoo min doonil laahi aalihatal liyakoonoo lahum 'izzaa
  19,82,Kallaa; sa yakfuroona bi'ibaadatihim wa yakoonoona 'alaihim diddaa (section 9)
  19,83,Alam tara annaaa arsalnash Shayaateena 'alal kaafireena ta'uzzuhum azzaa
  19,84,Falaa ta'jal alaihim innamaa na 'uddu lahum 'addaa
  19,85,Yawma nahshurul muttaqeena ilar Rahmaani wafdaa
  19,86,Wa nasooqul mujrimeena ilaa Jahannama wirdaa
  19,87,Laa yamlikoonash shafaa'ta illaa manittakhaza 'indar Rahmaani 'ahdaa
  19,88,Wa qaalut takhazar Rahmaanu waladaa
  19,89,Laqad ji'tum shai'an iddaa
  19,90,Takaadus samaawaatu yatafattarna minhu wa tanshaq qul ardu wa takhirrul jibaalu haddaa
  19,91,An da'aw lir Rahmaani waladaa
  19,92,Wa maa yambaghee lir Rahmaani ai yattakhiza waladaa
  19,93,In kullu man fis samaawaati wal ardi illaaa aatir Rahmaani 'abdaa
  19,94,Laqad ahsaahum wa addahum 'addaa
  19,95,Wa kulluhum aateehi Yawmal Qiyaamati fardaa
  19,96,Innal lazeena aamanoo wa 'amilus saalihaati sa yaj'alu lahumur Rahmaanu wuddaa
  19,97,Fa innamaa yassarnaahu bilisaanika litubashshira bihil muttaqeena wa tunzira bihee qawmal luddaa
  19,98,Wa kam ahlaknaa qabla hum min qarnin hal tuhissu minhum min ahadin aw tasma'u lahum rikzaa (section 6)
